Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:18.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:20.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainy Season Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:21.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quartz Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:26.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This story is fiction and it's not related to any real people, organizations or incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:52.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound can even wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dish from my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the one that's called miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cooked the same way the rockfish is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:29.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a little bit of miso that my mom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a lot, so please eat as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:48.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Communication has finally arrived from the people sending us supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go and retrieve them with Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:58.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ammunition, medicine and commodities. There should be a lot coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can finally breathe easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Noeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be in Karl's studio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be practicing the horn seriously this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad will cry if he sees you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here for you. Some teacakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these fortune cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look as if you still hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids at the church are innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:31.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. They just spread useless superstitions and tease for money. They are the same anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:37.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What we have here are the really delicious ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:41.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
