Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:53.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kana-chan seems to have gotten used to her life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always working hard. How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I do recognize her eagerness and seriousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't be so naive and think that she's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Se-cr-et.
