Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll be back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make trouble for Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Departure commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to do it at this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but using only the mouthpiece to control the tone is basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you find the life on the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:26.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way you declare it, it must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your optimism makes me a little bit envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did you join the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you can learn to play musical instruments for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:49.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-protecting the country is also very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It doesn't matter if you are doing it for money or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:59.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People with a clear purpose last longer than those without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why would Rio-senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was totally different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's pretty rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for the brass, because you probably won't even hear about it unless you are in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it... before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like... senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you! Hold on! Hold on, Kanata!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot? It's like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:29.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow... I wanna eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow. Where is the snow. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible to find it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... No. That can only be the last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:28.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine! Medicine! Medicine! Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots from the supply department!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMN!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Hi there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are any of the children bothering you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for all of my bad behavior before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a high fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she should be fine after drinking this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a serious illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's probably tertian malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tertian malaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a disease that only occurs in children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:59.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can also occur in adults if they are totally exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:07.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was common for children to get infected when they had just arrived at our church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common that those who seemed perfectly normal suddenly get a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:16.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have tried really hard to endure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:21.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Will Kanata recover from this completely? Will she be like this forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... Thank you very much... Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is made from herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have her drink this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... I am sorry for causing you all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Serving the people in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is our pleasure and responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also... May God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:14.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... am just the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That we drank in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:41.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:47.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miso-gasu... it's the bean residue left after miso is filtered out when making the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:54.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the unnecessary things, the unwanted things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:59.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was a kid, everyone called me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:05.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore this time, I tried my best not to be a burden on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:07.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it turns out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:14.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are much more fragile than you appear to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are self-willed and naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:25.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The music you just hummed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What music?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:07.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so amazing that you can recite it after hearing it only once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long long time ago... I heard it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought "It would be nice if I could play that song too."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:25.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,really want to play that heavenly music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:32.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that wherever it is, miso can only be miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to seek help from the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This Takemicaduchi is a treasure from the ancients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:47.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are lots of things hidden inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the details, ask Noeru later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This music...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably a complete version of that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:12.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the instruments, all of the parts are in harmony and form a complete song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same as driving a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:24.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, gunner, driver and communicator. Everyone dedicates their power to drive the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no redundant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unnecessary sounds do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that. I just repeated what I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:45.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the person I looked up to and respected the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:53.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that person's words, Kanata, do you know why senpai and superiors exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are here so the juniors have someone to trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:04.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't accomplish something, just keep your unwillingness and powerlessness in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:07.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also the warmth of being taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:14.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday when it is your turn to take care of others, all of these will become your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:21.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, feel free to trouble me. I did the same when I was a junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you are not doing well, you will be scolded and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:30.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, speak out if you find things difficult, and also when you feel they are too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:32.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:44.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will try my best and be sure to give you lots of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do be considerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...well. I should have just stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:05.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being looked after by Rio-senpai... geez that Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing special. She's just too exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let her sleep and she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemicaduchi was activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I am sorry. I just used it... Is there any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:30.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to hear that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:32.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you didn't want to hear that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:39.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:42.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:46.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
